ManualTypeDispatcher - Class in org.lfj.lang.util
This is a manual type dispatcher which allows you to dispatch types based upon a set of declared specs.
ManualTypeDispatcher(MemberSpec[], TypeDispatcher) - Constructor for class org.lfj.lang.util.ManualTypeDispatcher
Construct a manual type dispatcher from an array of declared specs and its fallback dispatcher to be used when there is no name matching specs among the declared specs.
